<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Teńdesi joq Uly Qudaı РӘЖ10 МЖЖ142 ҮРәж207</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.  F          Dm      Bb
 Teńdesi joq Uly Qudaı
.   C     F
 Sıynam Saǵan.
.  F            Dm
 Taǵzym etip kelgenimde
.  Bb         Gm   C
 Tynyshtyqqa bóleısiń.

[C1]
.  Bb    F        Dm      Bb   C
   Jan-dúnıemdi Táńirim Saǵan berem.
.  F            Dm     Bb     C   F
   Uly Qudaı ómirimniń bulaǵysyń Sen.

[V2]
 Aldyńa kelip, bas ıem,
 Táńirim, Saǵan.
 Jubanyshtyń jalǵyz kózin
 Taptym men tek Ózińnen.
 Ulysyń Sen,
 Teń keler jan joq Saǵan.
 Aldyńa kep tabynamyn,
 Meıirimdi Ákem.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<author>Don Moen</author>
